/*
OWNERSHIP TRANSFERRED
=====================

Transferred ownership to {{ data_product_name | upper }}_ADMIN:
- All {{ zone_list | length }} database(s) for data product {{ data_product_name }}
- All schemas within those databases

Naming Pattern: {{ object_component_order }}_<zone>

The owner role now:
- Owns all databases and schemas
- Controls all grants (managed access)
- Can delegate to ADMIN, WRITER, READER roles

SYSADMIN retains USAGE for troubleshooting.
*/